# MMS (ISO 9506) confirmed-request: Read, over the full TPKT/COTP/ISO-Session/Presentation stack.
# Real ICCP/TASE.2 PDU reassembled from a TCP-segmented capture (mms.cap frame 20, GetDataValue =
# MMS read); the reassembled TPKT PDU is re-wrapped in eth/IPv4/TCP:102 via the codec so checksums are
# correct. Only the hex is committed, never the pcap. MMS PDU: 61(fully-encoded-data) -> 30(PDV-list)
# -> 020103(context 3) -> a0(confirmed-request) -> 020211 50(invokeID 4432) -> a4(read [4]).

